Units : 
--------
1. Px = Pixel = Picture Element

Parent div
    |-- height : 200px
    |-- width : 500px 
    
Child div
    |-- height : 100px
    |-- width : 300px
    
On changing dimensions of parent : 
Parent div
    |-- height : 50px
    |-- width : 250px 
    
Child div dimension remains same
    |-- height : 100px
    |-- width : 300px

2. % percentage

    